{"tid":2439570,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"SM娛樂出新周邊「2度沒有Red Velvet款」　粉絲一看氣炸了！","createTime":"2021-03-09T10:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T01:24:25.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b3def644f079baaf0adc60a97ed5c4aced02c6ce","tid":2439570,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:42:20.000Z","msg":"南韓女團Red Velvet隊長Irene在10月底爆出罵哭造型師的私下霸道行徑，讓冰山美人的她形象大傷，沉寂了幾個月後，團體終於在2021年1月的SM家族演唱會中，以5人完整體現身，她更在1月中時在官方粉絲團Lysn上寫下長文道歉，怎料8日SM娛樂公開一組新的周邊商品，卻不見Red Velvet的設計，讓大批粉絲氣憤留言，引起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5491/5491847.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5491%2F5491847.jpg&h=c8140e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Red Velvet在SM家族演唱會上，久違地以5人完整體現身。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／Red Velvet）<br />\n<br />\nSM娛樂除了積極發展旗下藝人的演藝事業之外，周邊商品的設計也是主打之一，從一般的文具用品到以藝人簽名做成的飾品都有，8日公開一組全新彩色吊飾，吊牌的設計上有著團體的應援色、出道日以及相關圖案，總共有東方神起、SUPER JUNIOR、少女時代、SHINee、EXO、NCT 127、NCT DREAM、WayV、aespa 7組團體的設計。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5491/5491851.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5491%2F5491851.jpg&h=190013fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲SM推出新的周邊，卻缺少了Red Velvet的款式。（圖／翻攝自推特／SMTOWNandSTORE）<br />\n<br />\n怎料，SM娛樂推出的最新周邊曝光後，馬上被眼尖的網友發現少了Red Velvet的設計，火速引起大批粉絲討論，紛紛氣憤地留言「請問Red Velvet去哪了」、「為什麼沒有Red Velvet」、「這是認真的嗎？」、「有夠傻眼」、「真的不知道該說什麼了」，引起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5491/5491849.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5491%2F5491849.jpg&h=dd9e1c0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲SM推出的新周邊沒有Red Velvet的款式，引起粉絲熱議。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／Red Velvet）<br />\n<br />\n事實上，SM娛樂在2月推出一款包包周邊時，就被發現沒有Red Velvet的款式，只不過因為布質的包包上只繡了團體的第一個英文字母，簡約的設計看起來相較之下沒有太過明顯，但這一次新公開的吊飾上，則明顯缺少了Red Velvet的設計，引起更加引起網友討論，另外也有不少f(x)的歌迷跳出發言，難過地表示「我們都不知道被SM遺忘多久了」，語氣相當無奈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5491/5491850.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5491%2F5491850.jpg&h=d5aa1365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲SM娛樂2月推出的包包周邊，就沒有出現Red Velvet的款。（圖／翻攝自推特／SMTOWNandSTORE）"},{"pid":"7d30ec64a2fba2ce53e01517aea25ee716665dcf","tid":2439570,"uid":52073,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:44:22.000Z","msg":"我和溫溫做愛"},{"pid":"cf41538bf10c06aaeabc5bad75cfa554b0d5b153","tid":2439570,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d30ec64a2fba2ce53e01517aea25ee716665dcf","tid":2439570,"uid":52073,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:44:22.000Z","msg":"我和溫溫做愛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:44:48.000Z","msg":"人如其名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e31ea12b02a0876c4d43719f604486b90fee68","tid":2439570,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:51:30.000Z","msg":"sm食屎拉...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbeb1503402d819b4972acf4bc1e744ccd709380","tid":2439570,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d7e31ea12b02a0876c4d43719f604486b90fee68","tid":2439570,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:51:30.000Z","msg":"sm食屎拉...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:57:14.000Z","msg":"抵JYP然<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4243fa8d7e433ef834468088358bc6250c98a966","tid":2439570,"uid":294121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:58:03.000Z","msg":"閪女人累全家"},{"pid":"a336aa0203968e712acdb8818b7ce97605e0aff5","tid":2439570,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:58:54.000Z","msg":"Joy仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0054e08fa3db0c8da39438af1b340aee61ef36d9","tid":2439570,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike